s trembling frame, there remains a flicker of resilience, a silent plea for understanding in the depths of its wide, expressive eyes. In this delicate balance between captivity and longing, the scared chimp serves as a poignant reminder of the ethical complexities inherent in the pursuit of knowledge and the profound bond that unites all living beings in a shared journey of empathy and compassion.", "short_description": "In the confines of the research facility, amidst the cold metal and artificial light, a scared chimp resides, its once vibrant spirit subdued by the weight of captivity. Each day unfolds in a monotony of routines, its fur dulled and its movements marked by hesitancy as it navigates the sterile enclosure. Through the bars of its cage, it gazes longingly towards a world it can no longer touch, yearning for the freedom of its natural habitat. Yet, despite the fear that grips its trembling frame, th"}]}, "developer_name": "ChimpGames", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/scaredchimp1/home", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "ChimpGames", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/scaredchimp/home", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "961172191044986"}, {"id": "411892083130028"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "7134799263308720"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baselin